    dc:description "FIGURES 2−5. Adults of Eretmocera spp. 2, E. yingjiangensis sp. nov., a, holotype, ♂, b, paratype, ♂; 3, E. octopunctata sp. nov., a, holotype, ♂, b, paratype, ♀; 4, E. artemisiae sp. nov., a, holotype, ♂, b, paratype, ♀, c, paratype, ♀; 5, E. impactella, ♂. (Scale bars = 2.0 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3259274/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3259284>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23−25. Genitalia of Eretmocera impactella (Walker). 23, male genitalia, slide No. LK17075; 24, tergum VIII (up) and sternum (down), slide No. LK17075; 25, female genitalia, slide No. LK17204. (Scale bars = 0.25 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3259284/files/figure.png" ;
